[Bagpipe music] There are moments that seem bizarre, moments of fear … … preparation and moments of emptiness.
In China, a quarantined building collapses, and a firefighter breaks down after pulling bodies from the rubble.
In Australia, a run on toilet paper leads to lessons in self-defense.
Across rooftops in China, quarantined neighbors socialize.
This is how it is across the globe as we prepare, grieve and wait for the next chapter of the coronavirus.